A set of libraries for building tests for the CMS bitweaver

Required Dependencies:
Install PHPUnit with PEAR
pear channel-discover pear.phpunit.de
pear install phpunit/PHPUnit

Install:
$ cd <bitweaver_root_dir>
$ git clone git://github.com/tekimaki/bwtestsuite.git

Sample PHPUnit test case included, to run:
$ cd bwtestsuite/phpunit
$ phpunit --testdox SampleTestCase


